Package: ggbasemap
Type: Package
Title: Add Basemap Tiles to ggplot2
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Cédric", "Bouffard", email = "info@cedricbouffard.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a function to add basemap tiles from XYZ tile servers
    to ggplot2 plots. Automatically detects bounding boxes and calculates
    appropriate zoom levels.
